data.description: Welcome home to this charming property! As you enter, you'll be greeted by a cozy fireplace, perfect for those chilly evenings. The natural color palette throughout the home creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. The spacious kitchen features a center island, offering plenty of counter space for meal prepping and entertaining. With other rooms available for flexible living space, you'll have the freedom to create a suit your needs. The primary bathroom boasts a separate tub and shower, providing a luxurious and relaxing experience. Double sinks and good under sink storage add convenience and functionality. Step outside to the backyard and discover a serene sitting area where you can unwind and enjoy the fresh air. With fresh interior paint, this home feels bright and rejuvenated. Don't miss out on this incredible property.
